      "angle": "The transition from human-driven retail meme trading to machine-to-machine commerce.",
      "whyItMatters": "The transition from human-driven retail meme trading to machine-to-machine commerce.",
      "sources": [
        "https://m.theblockbeats.info/news/61489",
